gov.usgs.anss.ewexport

Class EWExportOutputer

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • gov.usgs.anss.ewexport.EWExportOutputer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class EWExportOutputer
extends java.lang.Thread
    This class empties a TraceBufQueue which is filled by a EWExportSocket thread. This actually sends the data, limits the bandwidth usage to avoid going too fast for EW rings in a catch up situation. It starts the EWHeartBeatHandler which sends out heartbeats at the prescribed rate, and receives heartbeats and implements the heart beat timeout when heart beats in do not arrive.
